{"tid":768513,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"剛分手嘅你點振作？","createTime":"2018-08-05T12:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T02:47:40.000Z","uid":122600,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"26806c4c63425e50885efc8286becaf3490e5168","tid":768513,"uid":122600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:49:24.000Z","msg":"分手前已經冷戰咗一排，但我仲好傻咁寄咗份禮物畀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上星期正式分手，佢一直冇講分手兩隻字，我冇晒尊嚴咁不斷哀求都冇用，佢話唔識同我相處 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾日已經del晒合照 fb 同block ig<br />\n但我仲喺個傷心嘅漩渦裡面來來回回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一時自責 一時嬲 一時掛住<br />\n見到佢好似好開心嘅生活，同人有講有笑<br />\n好辛苦 好想死<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利申真絲"},{"pid":"f4622d5b8c5e2691f4917217cc975b2d070f44ae","tid":768513,"uid":185165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:51:09.000Z","msg":"叫鴨解憂愁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393eb2f3db6f426f3a54c6bec21132a645ffeedf","tid":768513,"uid":197954,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:53:24.000Z","msg":"不停搵野做黎分散自己注意力<br />\n想喊就喊 好好發洩下"},{"pid":"ae0e4a1e64cb4330b5f21781f5f48620934f3496","tid":768513,"uid":65051,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:53:30.000Z","msg":"只可以講時間會令你淡忘<br />\n但無辦法會忘記。"},{"pid":"4daef4b0d78bf690cf84451ecf182402c361a8c2","tid":768513,"uid":4647,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:55:54.000Z","msg":"講出嚟會舒服啲嘅<br />\n<br />\n不過千祈唔好以為對方會回心轉意"},{"pid":"c3e6180f8ee130e7fa3f68f05f1dc0535036c304","tid":768513,"uid":141837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:57:14.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"df269816888f1775559cca4ea342930e4b4279cd","tid":768513,"uid":122600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4daef4b0d78bf690cf84451ecf182402