<br />\n<br />\n加油阿絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b1de802638b6945d6e71afc1b8e693d4353dc4","tid":768513,"uid":64479,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:36:58.000Z","msg":"啱啱分手就快一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢可以無縫接軌同第三者一齊<br />\n我喺街撞正佢地拖手個幕 真係求心理陰影面積<br />\n依家發夢都會夢到佢地 好大打擊<br />\n唯有見多啲朋友 盡量報多啲更翻工分散下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1874fd1e068cab6b9631a8a8d41bc9e8179a93","tid":768513,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:40:04.000Z","msg":"無振作過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9a11d20a0ecd794b972f44e98cd3f0a3f2a271","tid":768513,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90b1de802638b6945d6e71afc1b8e693d4353dc4","tid":768513,"uid":64479,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:36:58.000Z","msg":"啱啱分手就快一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢可以無縫接軌同第三者一齊<br />\n我喺街撞正佢地拖手個幕 真係求心理陰影面積<br />\n依家發夢都會夢到佢地 好大打擊<br />\n唯有見多啲朋友 盡量報多啲更翻工分散下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:41:30.000Z","msg":"咁癲.. 撞到既話我估我抖唔到氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848223ba9c534fbbca7149800d56c16e4ce48d36","tid":768513,"uid":102493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"我都係 拍左六年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e93afbf73c8ce46d319f92eff3762ced857eb1e","tid":768513,"uid":108304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:43:16.000Z","msg":"麻煩你傷我心"},{"pid":"fde1f4469e1fa9b36a41bedb5a76fe9b29e14fbd","tid":768513,"uid":64479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af9a11d20a0ecd794b972f44e98cd3f0a3f2a271","tid":768513,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90b1de802638b6945d6e71afc1b8e693d4353dc4","tid":768513,"uid":64479,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:36:58.000Z","msg":"啱啱分手就快一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢可以無縫接軌同第三者一齊<br />\n我喺街撞正佢地拖手個幕 真係求心理陰影面積<br />\n依家發夢都會夢到佢地 好大打擊<br />\n唯有見多啲朋友 盡量報多啲更翻工分散下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:41:30.000Z","msg":"咁癲.. 撞到既話我估我抖唔到氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:48:07.000Z","msg":"未講分手之前已經有朋友撞到佢係街拖住第二條女 <br />\n我即刻講分手 佢唔認偷食仲講到自己同條女好清白無任何關係 到最後係街自己親眼撞到個下 我成個人係好激動<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ef59a332e2a0978fe9884af974753c493118cd","tid":768513,"uid":126420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"848223ba9c534fbbca7149800d56c16e4ce48d36","tid":768513,"uid":102493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"我都係 拍左六年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:50:23.000Z","msg":"6 年.... 發生咩事？"},{"pid":"547ca8f33ecd963068182a348cabb4e713796e99","tid":768513,"uid":160378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:06:26.000Z","msg":"7月中分手 一開頭真係日日喊咁濟<br />\n日日聽&lt;下次愛你&gt; &lt;我的天&gt; &lt;說散就散&gt; &lt;你有心&gt;<br />\n不斷loop 每次聽親都諗起佢 行過同佢去過嘅地方就諗起佢 每日都想揾佢 但去到宜家 呢種感覺冇咁強烈<br />\n因為覺得無論你點做都係冇撚用 因為佢個心唔係到 <br />\n咁點解仲要冇尊嚴咁求返對方<br />\n分咗手一星期之後我問佢要唔要一份以前整咗嘅禮物 佢覆:唔洗啦你留住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問一句:屌你老母你幾時死 壓力？我幾時俾過壓力你？好攰要休息下？你攰乜撚？時間唔夠用兼顧唔到咁多嘢就打少啲機啦 分手都要將個責任推落我到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  男人嚟架？話鐘意我？乜鐘意一個人原來咁易放棄？屌你老母 死大陸仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我仲等緊仲期待緊有一日你會揾返我<br />\n你返轉頭嘅話 我會同你講一句:我一直都等緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd38f7d8d40356f5961bf3439a9cbd24436f338","tid":768513,"uid":88723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:32:20.000Z","msg":"迫自己接受佢唔愛你既事實 <br />\n佢絕對無可能番轉頭<br />\n比自己頹廢幾日可以盡量諗佢盡情喊<br />\n再死捱爛捱<br />\n過左一排 就無咁痛了"},{"pid":"4b1ca34d3a4e5d53a54226ac21282aebd7564a4c","tid":768513,"uid":122600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"547ca8f33ecd963068182a348cabb4e713796e99","tid":768513,"uid":160378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:06:26.000Z","msg":"7月中分手 一開頭真係日日喊咁濟<br />\n日日聽&lt;下次愛你&gt; &lt;我的天&gt; &lt;說散就散&gt; &lt;你有心&gt;<br />\n不斷loop 每次聽親都諗起佢 行過同佢去過嘅地方就諗起佢 每日都想揾佢 但去到宜家 呢種感覺冇咁強烈<br />\n因為覺得無論你點做都係冇撚用 因為佢個心唔係到 <br />\n咁點解仲要冇尊嚴咁求返對方<br />\n分咗手一星期之後我問佢要唔要一份以前整咗嘅禮物 佢覆:唔洗啦你留住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問一句:屌你老母你幾時死 壓力？我幾時俾過壓力你？好攰要休息下？你攰乜撚？時間唔夠用兼顧唔到咁多嘢就打少啲機啦 分手都要將個責任推落我到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  男人嚟架？話鐘意我？乜鐘意一個人原來咁易放棄？屌你老母 死大陸仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我仲等緊仲期待緊有一日你會揾返我<br />\n你返轉頭嘅話 我會同你講一句:我一直都等緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:41:28.000Z","msg":"Same here<img src=\"/asset